page.title: 13Penny's Days 2
page.content: Got back from school I went into the living room and took off my jacket . Watched a t.v. programme called 'The Young Doctors.' Went to the toilet. Watched a t.v. progamme called 'Crystal Tips and Alastair.','Emu's world ' and the 'Joke Machine.' Then I had tea, I had two pork pies, chips and beans. After that I had a very small piece of swiss roll and a drink of water. Watched a t.v. programme called 'Take the High Road.' Did a number puzzle and watched the 'Zodiac Game' and a programme called 'Cover-Up.' Went to bed at haf past eight and did puzzles until half nine.
